---
full_description:

Are you ready for the next generation of orchestration platforms? **Temporal** is the successor to [Uber Cadence](https://cadenceworkflow.io/). It is an open source, distributed, and scalable workflow orchestration platform to execute mission-critical business logic with resilience. Your code will run reliably even if it encounters problems, such as network outages or server crashes. With great Developer Experience (DX) and [Python SDK](https://docs.temporal.io/develop/python), the platform simplifies coding. Join us to unlock the power of Python and Temporal in mastering workflow orchestration!
